{"word":"ἀγεννής","slug":"ἀγεννής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγεννής</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:γέννα'><el>γέννα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>of no family, low-born</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>low-minded</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of things, much like <el>βάναυσος</el>, <i>illiberal, sordid</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>; <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-νῶς</el>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}